<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-20-1076 </DOCNO><TEXT>Renewable energy is one of four technology areas for joint RD andamp; D efforts,and wind energy is generally considered one of the most promising ofthe renewable energies. Two Agreements on wind energy were implementedin 1977: a program for research and development on wind energy conversionsystems (IEA R andamp; D WECS) and cooperation in the development of large-scalewind energy conversion systems (IEA LS WECS). Progress under both programsis discussed.</TEXT></DOC>